Css propertys 

Set a bg 
Body{
	Background-image: url (image url .ext );
	Background-size:cover;
}

Remove dots from li opjects 

Li{
	Liost-style: none;
}


Changing mouse cursor to pointer when hovering 

H2{
	Cursor : pointer;
}

To make more than one thing have the same css class we use 
Somting like 
H2 , p{
	Color: red;
} 

